{"tid":692653,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"半獨遊 九日八夜倫敦鳩fing之遊 (唔多圖又唔多字)","createTime":"2018-06-07T00:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T08:01:34.000Z","uid":143366,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"675a001cc4d81467c51da1e358e4d3c31f9c6bfa","tid":692653,"uid":143366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T00:28:27.000Z","msg":"依次係我第一次係到開post開遊記<br />\n但係未知細佬我咁玩法咁多連登仔會唔會屌鳩我hea 玩得唔盡興<br />\n不過唔知點解都係好想開個post紀錄低佢<br />\n大家唔岩睇嘅就負皮上一頁啦<br />\n講明先 頭幾個post應該會係informative啲<br />\n去過嘅可以飛左佢 直接睇遊記部份<br />\n廢話唔多講 依家開波<br />\n<br />\n行程如下:<br />\nDay 1: Euston落車-&gt; German Gymnasium食晏-&gt; 攪啲私事-&gt; Check In-&gt; settle啲行李-&gt; Fishworks食夜晚-&gt; 完<br />\nDay 2: 白金漢宮睇Change of guards-&gt; 兜住白金漢宮鳩fing-&gt; Royal Mews-&gt; 係去Westminster途中鳩fing-&gt; Westminster-&gt; London Eye(冇上到去)附近鳩fing-&gt; 完<br />\nDay 3: Windsor castle-&gt; 附近鳩fing-&gt; Bizzaro 食夜晚-&gt; 完<br />\nDay 4: Aquashard 食晏-&gt; British Museum 行到閉館-&gt; Wagamama 食夜晚-&gt; 係KCL鳩fing<br />\nDay 5: Tower Bridge-&gt; La Dame de Pic 食晏-&gt; Tower of London-&gt; Tate Modern-&gt; 完<br />\nDay 6: 搭船去Greenwich-&gt; Cutty Sark-&gt; Royal Observatory-&gt; 搭船返倫敦-&gt; 完<br />\nDay 7: 係KCL附近食晏-&gt; 係Somerset House個畫廊行左陣-&gt; Hyde Park餵雀-&gt; Harrods行陣街-&gt; Zuma 食夜晚-&gt; 完<br />\nDay 8: Sexy Fish食晏-&gt; Hatchards買書-&gt; Fortnum &amp; Mason買茶葉同餅乾-&gt; charbonnel et walker 買朱古力-&gt; Laduree 買Macaron-&gt; 再去Harrods行街-&gt; Dinner by Heston Blumenthal 食夜晚-&gt; 完<br />\nDay 9: Hea到下晏3 4點-&gt; Convent Garden-&gt; GBK食夜晚-&gt; 9點走人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講下大家最開心嘅機票同住宿先<br />\n其實我係直接由Manchester過去 本身有啲私事要做左先所以就過左man<br />\n如果想知飛Man嘅機票係點嘅話覺得你直接上skyscanner睇仲快<br />\n因為細佬我要顧埋同我一齊係man返嘅人<br />\n所以張機票都唔係最平又唔係最快<br />\n<br />\n住我係住Airbnb 依間我都幾推薦大家去住 價錢方面包哂所有野都係466一晚<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/080919_e3f93b5c522ed762d4c1d7bafbc15dad.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F080919_e3f93b5c522ed762d4c1d7bafbc15dad.PNG&h=a703235e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係正Marylebone隔離<br />\n唔鐘意Marylebone要轉車嘅 行5分鐘就去到Baker Street 交通都幾方便<br />\n個host好好人 唔會嘈住你<br />\n佢一開波話佢自己係你Roommate多過係land lady<br />\n如果大家去倫敦嘅話都可以去 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁去到倫敦就要攪返張oyster先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/081711_42d2c442d284e25508492c90c0ccf135.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F081711_42d2c442d284e25508492c90c0ccf135.JPG&h=3b2d6fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為係倫敦搭車都貴 係zone 1(central london) 一程都要2.4磅<br />\n所以一開波入20磅都可以 橫掂一定唔夠用<br />\n反而退deposit方面就要小心啲 係車站啲增值機到都有得退<br />\n好似八達通咁係有得退 但係如果你張Oyster餘額多過10磅就會退唔到<br />\n所以大家最好計岩條數<br />\n同埋搭車大家記住睇實尾班車係幾點<br />\n細佬我有兩次爭啲返唔到屋企 大家小心少少<br />\n<br />\n退稅方面 你去大型啲嘅鋪頭 例如Harrods / Harvey Nichols 都會有<br />\n但係記住帶埋身份證<br />\n你可以退落信用卡又得退現金又得 我相信個櫃檯小姐會清楚過我<br />\n放膽啲去問就得架啦"},{"pid":"3e74e3f607bf02dedcc0633a8839a3ff96f89678","tid":692653,"uid":33777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T02:56:16.000Z","msg":"lm爛尾"},{"pid":"dbe70e2cf489d13c395426eba6024cc17ee6784e","tid":692653,"uid":143366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:22:41.000Z","msg":"戴定頭盔先 細佬我影相唔得掂之餘仲要係用ip6s+影 <br />\n所以依個post應該唔會出現啲咩「樓主用咩影」呱<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 29/5:<br />\n係開始之先要同大家講下咩係Railcard先<br />\nrailcard你當佢係一年制會員 你買左佢會籍先可以係Trainline到買到平飛<br />\n佢有幾種 如果你係學生(16-25歲)佢有種16-25railcard 一年30磅 冇得退嘅<br />\n就咁聽上去會有啲貴 但係如果你打算由London去埋Bath或者其他地方嘅話\\<br />\nrailcard pricecut已經大過30磅 所以大家要自己衡量下自己洗唔洗買啦<br />\n如果要買嘅話 係各大火車站 記住唔係地鐵站 都會有得賣<br />\n<br />\n朝早搭火車由Man去London Euston<br />\n我啲朋友一直話佢地唔會睇你張railcard<br />\n可能係我柒啦 條友係有問我有冇railcard嘅<br />\n但係只要你態度好啲打下人情牌 可能個職員會俾你過<br />\n仲記得個職員話今次俾個benefit of doubt我<br />\n落車之後好去買返張啦 俾人捉到要補差價就唔係30磅咁簡單架啦<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/084126_8642ebf5a4fa30ab03b10a149f247855.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F084126_8642ebf5a4fa30ab03b10a149f247855.JPG&h=7a6798c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家去倫敦嘅要注意下有啲轉車站佢啲 車立 可能淨係停其中一條線<br />\n例如convent garden嘅 piccadilly / jubliee line咁 所以大家一抽二lung嘅時候要睇清楚<br />\n<br />\n因為一落車佢落緊大雨加上我拖住行李 所以就冇影到相<br />\n依家直接帶大家去到German Gymnasium<br />\n(係到貼條link俾大家自己去睇睇 <a href=\"https://www.germangymnasium.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.germangymnasium.com%2F&d=qIAbQZyuGOXVpkIC6F%2FZ8CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=cc0e3f77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.germangymnasium.com/</a>)<br />\n原身為purpose-built gym嘅Grade-2 Building 佢入邊嘅裝潢係真係唔錯<br />\n但係可能因為個位址真係太好 午餐時間係多人嘅<br />\n亦都係因為咁 我都唔好意思郁身郁勢去影相<br />\n餐廳個bar都唔錯 大家去嘅話不妨嗌杯酒<br />\n我就咁嗌左杯Elderflower and citrus Gin and Tonic 真係唔錯<br />\nbtw倫敦甚至全英國都會成日見到gin 無論平時有飲開嘅定係貪新鮮嘅都可以試下<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/191618_6dea3999e0a7fea875a626f9949146be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F191618_6dea3999e0a7fea875a626f9949146be.jpg&h=10e1469d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總括而言 成個vibe都係唔錯 係啲位冇咁好坐<br />\n<br />\n去到野食部份<br />\n前菜我嗌左個Bayrisher Wurstalat<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/190824_e6e6519a7e0898833fd9d0e898cce41f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F190824_e6e6519a7e0898833fd9d0e898cce41f.jpg&h=e0a60324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(啲相全部打橫哂所以要crop過哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n個沙律都唔錯嘅 我諗係一個人食太大份<br />\n食到後半就唔多想食<br />\n大家想去嘅可以同朋友一齊去 試多幾個菜<br />\n主菜就嗌左個Citrus Marinated poached Salmon<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/07/191828_133f0ea2ceed2d5b5a862b94943aff08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F07%2F191828_133f0ea2ceed2d5b5a862b94943aff08.jpg&h=8c5d4f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一樣啦 都係食到後半就會唔想食 可能係前一日肚痛影響胃口<br />\n反而細佬注意嘅係佢上碟嘅時候係冇抹乾淨隻碟 觀感上係扣左啲分嘅<br />\n但係都係推薦大家去試下佢個bar嘅<br />\n<br />\n講住餐晏仔先"},{"pid":"14129daa510da4ddd6a29c66e93062e2793660a1","tid":692653,"uid":143366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e74e3f607bf02dedcc0633a8839a3ff96f89678","tid":692653,"uid":33777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T02:56:16.000Z","msg":"lm爛尾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"應該唔會呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔求多人睇 只係想做個紀錄"},{"pid":"498a687e4f2a5415fda993b1d8f9e0199c9dc258","tid":692653,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T15:15:29.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c972714d4d356dfc593403a4e4be9143f7ecf47e","tid":692653,"uid":131955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"大站答火車梗係會check飛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b230db09a64787d1db81a94c49d5f42812e44f8d","tid":692653,"uid":143366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:31:58.000Z","msg":"Day 1 續:<br />\nHea下hea下就到8點<br />\n聽個host講Marylebone有間食魚嘅叫fishwork幾出名<br />\n如果咁岩你睇到依個post又諗住去試下嘅<br />\n我會話︰「咪撚去。」<br />\n<br />\n俾住啲圖大家睇先 再等我娓娓道來<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/081035_3ec230f0d619d24d00f9ce90ea05f8cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F081035_3ec230f0d619d24d00f9ce90ea05f8cd.jpg&h=0c5fcca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能我淨係可以試到佢一道菜 未能試到佢全貌<br />\n但係一道 oven-baked sea bass可以做到佢咁都係一個值得嘉許嘅地方<br />\n魚冇魚味 但係佢又冇落調味<br />\n我本身唔係食得好重口味 但係依條魚就真係bland as fuck<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/081445_261619d64da397885cd8452ff15e3843.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F081445_261619d64da397885cd8452ff15e3843.jpg&h=00bdca1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唯一一個好處就係佢有得俾你簡原條上抑或係filleted咁上<br />\n<br />\n另外佢個double-cooked fries都唔得掂<br />\n一上菜就已經係淋哂<br />\n同我係英國食到嘅其他薯條就相差甚遠<br />\n<br />\n總括而言 依間就真係唔洗試<br />\n留返啲錢去食間好食嘅fish and chips過下癮仲好過啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/082557_300a7749e4d995fb42f2ae6ba12178e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F082557_300a7749e4d995fb42f2ae6ba12178e6.jpg&h=e6e86338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順帶一提 如果大家係sherlock holmes嘅書迷<br />\n咁我諗你地可能會想去下佢個museum<br />\n提提大家 Baker St. 221b唔係真係順住門號就搵得到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/083012_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F083012_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=81501a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家要行多兩步先至到221B 搵唔到就睇下google map就得架啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 完。"},{"pid":"7eaa9fab43c713314a506d8f087ee0e8d97c73f9","tid":692653,"uid":143366,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c972714d4d356dfc593403a4e4be9143f7ecf47e","tid":692653,"uid":131955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"大站答火車梗係會check飛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:33:29.000Z","msg":"冇錯呀<br />\n但係就係想提下諗住搏大霧嘅大家呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d726bf37d87727d92ec56c4ae2db54f13ead3e66","tid":692653,"uid":87311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T00:38:56.000Z","msg":"樓主咁都叫鳩fing?<br />\n我去倫敦一日只行一個景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要hea 行<br />\n朝早行完夜晚去Club fing! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e67a26a4b666651f4c8d274960729629e2569d","tid":692653,"uid"