faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"你食果 d 呢?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"晏就都要40磅一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚就差唔多100<br />\n但係當然可以去食個快餐或者Nando&rsquo;s <br />\n嗰啲就十零磅咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"519ab69725b40e450636f4abbd528c0c87a5953b","tid":692653,"uid":143366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T00:27:18.000Z","msg":"Day 2:<br />\n依一日嘅重點就係朝早嘅change of guards<br />\n係個網站上面就寫話官方正式開始時間係11點鐘<br />\n<a href=\"https://changing-guard.com/dates-buckingham-palace.html#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchanging-guard.com%2Fdates-buckingham-palace.html%23&d=qIAbQZyuGOXVpkIC6F%2FZ8CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f4e58605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://changing-guard.com/dates-buckingham-palace.html#</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/080355_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F080355_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=0fad786a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係其實係開始之前已經會有啲「非正式」嘅小型步操 都推薦大家去睇下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/080536_61ac78cc639adcb07dd3f295fffcdd5f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F080536_61ac78cc639adcb07dd3f295fffcdd5f.JPG&h=91729890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(依張相係10:45影)<br />\n亦都係因為咁樣 就算我早左半個鐘去 前面都仲係有一大堆人一早到左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果大家想霸個靚位 咁就要早少少到啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/080850_228ed7207cf2cefd75117fc192ab993f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F080850_228ed7207cf2cefd75117fc192ab993f.jpg&h=d8900b85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個呀叔好撚英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n成個change of guards全程歷時9個字左右<br />\n但係你會見到廿分鐘左右就會有人走<br />\n有耐性嘅你不妨留多一陣 睇多兩眼 再等少人啲冇咁逼先走都得<br />\n因為最精彩嘅其實係最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/081752_108109337e8d167b9b4c3fcc0fe7d522.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F081752_108109337e8d167b9b4c3fcc0fe7d522.png&h=3c69d470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁個change of guards就各一段落啦<br />\n既然一程去到Buckingham Palace就梗係想一探究竟架啦<br />\n但係我係冇入到去嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢唔係日日開 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.royalcollection.org.uk/visit/the-state-rooms-buckingham-palace?gclid=EAIaIQobChMIpp7lnu3M2wIVr7_tCh3kWgbuEAAYASAAEgJJr_D_BwE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.royalcollection.org.uk%2Fvisit%2Fthe-state-rooms-buckingham-palace%3Fgclid%3DEAIaIQobChMIpp7lnu3M2wIVr7_tCh3kWgbuEAAYASAAEgJJr_D_BwE&d=qIAbQZyuGOXVpkIC6F%2FZ8CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b5422215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.royalcollection.org.uk/visit/the-state-rooms-buckingham-palace?gclid=EAIaIQobChMIpp7lnu3M2wIVr7_tCh3kWgbuEAAYASAAEgJJr_D_BwE</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/082109_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F082109_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=c13a2906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所以咁多位記住查定白金漢宮同佢周圍啲野有冇開<br />\n<br />\n即使如此 大家都可以係Green Park同Palace到鳩fing<br />\n都好多野睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/082439_8bca8ef3833218978052abd9b6729474.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F082439_8bca8ef3833218978052abd9b6729474.JPG&h=9d820e56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/082550_6b4b4881599fffe7ec557151cbe5dbeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F082550_6b4b4881599fffe7ec557151cbe5dbeb.jpg&h=2eba939f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦依章係咁多先 下章就講下Green Park附近行左啲咩"},{"pid":"dfe03d8d37310a3ad07fe9115e527c4a36cbdaae","tid":692653,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:55:56.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06096df8efbdb505c82ae6aabd4e0cabee70e31","tid":692653,"uid":94465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:57:20.000Z","msg":"倫敦多唔多人踩單車？"},{"pid":"1078d1adefe6bc324fb18026c78ca14e40abd185","tid":692653,"uid":143366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e06096df8efbdb505c82ae6aabd4e0cabee70e31","tid":692653,"uid":94465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:57:20.000Z","msg":"倫敦多唔多人踩單車？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T19:39:31.000Z","msg":"都多㗎<br />\n仲會有啲人係懶型咁踩單轆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}